CryptoWatcher ("we", "our", "us") operates the CryptoWatcher Discord bot and dashboard platform.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information:

Discord User ID

Discord Username

Role information

Commands used

Portfolio data entered by the user

Watchlist preferences

We do NOT collect:

Passwords

Private keys

Wallet seed phrases

Financial account credentials

2. How We Use Information

We use collected data to:

Provide premium features

Manage access levels

Track portfolio statistics

Improve system performance

Prevent abuse

3. Data Storage

Data is stored locally or on secured hosting infrastructure.
We implement reasonable safeguards to protect data.

4. Data Sharing

We do not sell or share user data with third parties.
Data may only be shared if legally required.

5. Financial Disclaimer

CryptoWatcher provides informational and analytical tools only.
We do not provide financial advice.

6. User Rights

Users may request deletion of stored data by contacting support.

7. Changes

We may update this policy at any time. Continued use implies acceptance.
